        android:layout_marginRight="5dp"
        android:textColor="#000006"
       	
       
        android:text="*2- The emergence of innate knowledge\n\n2-1 The mind is mantra.\n2-2 Effort leads to attainment.\n2-3 The secret of mantra is the being of the body of knowledge.\n2-4 The emergence of the mind in the womb is the forgetting of\ncommon knowledge.\n2-5 When the knowledge of one's self arises one moves in the\nsky of consciousness---the Shiva's state.\n2-6 The guru is the means.\n2-7 Awakened knowledge is the circle of the letters of the alphabet.\n2-8 The body is the oblation.\n2-9 The food is knowledge.\n2-10 With the extinction of knowledge emerges the vision of emptiness."/>

	
    	


 
    

